welcome_message_body: Welcome to Benbrook, where the charm of small-town living meets the excitement of city life. Get ready to experience our beautiful parks, delicious restaurants, and friendly community. We invite you to explore and make unforgettable memories in our wonderful city.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Meacham Field Airport, serving both domestic and international flights.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: A separate terminal for private and chartered flights at Meacham Field Airport.

wifi.note: Free wifi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Addison Airport offers a variety of amenities for travelers, including dining options, retail stores, and rental car services.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Addison Airport caters to private and corporate aircraft, providing luxurious amenities such as private lounges and concierge services.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Arlington Municipal Airport offers a variety of amenities for travelers, including a cafe, gift shop, and rental car services.

terminals.name: Private Terminal
terminals.description: The private terminal at Arlington Municipal Airport caters to executive and private jet travelers, offering luxurious lounge areas and concierge services.

wifi.note: Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the airport.

terminals.name: Main Terminal
terminals.description: The main terminal at Fort Worth Alliance Airport offers a variety of services and amenities for travelers.

wifi.note: Free WiFi is available throughout the airport.
